{"tid":450574,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考DSE嘅你冇必要去「探路」","createTime":"2017-10-28T10:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T15:15:23.000Z","uid":7109,"like":24,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f75ee8897cebad747234583b4e2bb198a05d07ab","tid":450574,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"出凖考證嗰時總有成班人話要去探路乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用下google揾定路，睇下間學校喺邊，真係難行嘅先去一次<br />\n考DSE之前每一日都好撚珍貴，之前揾定路+考試前早啲出門口 &gt; 浪費時間去所謂探路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f1fb60572bb1af7bf81b3b354dec7b0e3b1f38","tid":450574,"uid":132507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出凖考證嗰時總有成班人話要去探路乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用下google揾定路，睇下間學校喺邊，真係難行嘅先去一次<br />\n考DSE之前每一日都好撚珍貴，之前揾定路+考試前早啲出門口 &gt; 浪費時間去所謂探路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無， 坐地鐵到附近 call的士去"},{"pid":"c8ff444486674427e2dc533086bc7bf9a4ce71d9","tid":450574,"uid":142212,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:52:04.000Z","msg":"其實探路都係半日時間 阻得幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137b221776a3ef550c5e12f0b73ffbe9044555f9","tid":450574,"uid":6964,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"個朝搵唔到仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b649833424159650cdeb07188f68c31fd83ceba","tid":450574,"uid":12828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:58:08.000Z","msg":"可以有幾難行，又唔係山卡啦，睇下google街景咪夠"},{"pid":"8ec1392ffb84067dafb82dc71814aa38cde348ea","tid":450574,"uid":66158,"like":21,"dislike":13,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"又GPS又google map咁撚方便 <br />\n咁都要探路不如唔好撚考啦 你智商唔係好啱繼續讀書"},{"pid":"773d60df72867af35e49c39f624a57144dd6b531","tid":450574,"uid":127075,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"到個日是但搵條後生女問佢係咪去個度考dse就得啦"},{"pid":"2cb4670f5f888540708c1b2239f52cbe83316e33","tid":450574,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以有幾難行，又唔係山卡啦，睇下google街景咪夠</blockquote><br />\n喺屋村入面嗰啲就真係要行一行<br />\n其他就不了"},{"pid":"278250cea911abb5bae769f22074574d3b8e0109","tid":450574,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"你覺得冇必要咪唔好去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cede401bcbaa82094c334afa70092c0f4677831a","tid":450574,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"你覺得冇必要咪唔好去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3cd880815bdd9a1b1c1d5b7e44c8601c207d57","tid":450574,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"吓，坐開的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21aaefaf682b3016dc388451526a9ad21178b0c","tid":450574,"uid":33631,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"人地鍾意點關你撚事咩<br />\n又唔係影響到你"},{"pid":"b2fab67fca7cd52f1be7b31706ec1c45d068df65","tid":450574,"uid":14214,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:11:16.000Z","msg":"屌你啦<br />\n探路係以防考嗰日先發現原本路線係唔通<br />\n就算無真係遲到都嚇一嚇<br />\n<br />\n利申 當年好彩有探路<br />\n發現有間學校唔係想像中咁行<br />\n真係去考嗰時免受驚嚇/比預期遲到"},{"pid":"972f8f0716339e948b9b0155d9cb0106fd2a48e0","tid":450574,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:13:29.000Z","msg":"我話冇必要姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06006023cef0ce86af8f3c2366c21883ae2b58a3","tid":450574,"uid":31752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:24:50.000Z","msg":"兩樣都唔同意<br />\n探路無用係真<br />\n不過一日半日有幾撚珍貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45afc1c3401692ffd8630e51b3eafd4e05c50540","tid":450574,"uid":15730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:29:44.000Z","msg":"唔係自己果區啲考場就最好探下路既"},{"pid":"0006b69fac0a801bf211a4c7d96988053915f5d5","tid":450574,"uid":93046,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"如果一日半日真係咁緊要，咁你不如唔好考啦，你實力都係得咁多"},{"pid":"07e1574f2e1cc5a726ab1111bbc3cee5d9b028c9","tid":450574,"uid":117009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:37:13.000Z","msg":"年年都有人去錯考場"},{"pid":"73e1471e6c5e62e50ad2829d3cc70dfdb34bf0a4","tid":450574,"uid":66527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>年年都有人去錯考場</blockquote><br />\n樓主"},{"pid":"4335e28f7d9552e5b513ae8c5a36af012bffcf44","tid":450574,"uid":4213,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:39:42.000Z","msg":"探完你班垃圾咪又係入唔到HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全無探路意識<br />\nHKU First Hon"},{"pid":"e1358f40d4049afad65350616d5ef741f05ddfba","tid":450574,"uid":49974,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"上年考ict去將軍澳間咩真道書院考，搭地鐵出咗閘之後睇google諗住好快到，跟住條路行就得，行行下點撚知唔對路，離遠望先見到原來間學校係喺山上面嗰一層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後是鳩彈入咗個屋邨商場諗住可以上到去嗰一層，但入到去啲指示完全唔清晰，鳩行咗幾分鐘先見到馬路出返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好喇，行行下終於見到＂真道書院＂哩四隻字（亦即係啱啱係山下面見到嗰間），但係喺正門完全見唔到有任何考評局嘅指示，心諗已經覺得好奇怪，唔通記錯日子？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住有個保安行過嚟話哩間係小學部嚟，你要去中學部嘅話要再行上條斜路，真係畀佢激撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚彩最後都可以早十幾分鐘到，如果唔係真係好撚大獲，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7acea365722c5f4dc1d15c1e1672540701302c3","tid":450574,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:48:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7da90e0a4fc93c8074bb44554176260cce79e2ad","tid":450574,"uid":60115,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"讀書唔成嘅人探路去報asshole走後門最實際"},{"pid":"5e01121877e8e5c9059d3d3a7e5ed2747b10980f","tid":450574,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書唔成嘅人探路去報asshole走後門最實際</blockquote><br />\n一放榜就即刻狗衝去報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60650a8e4f99d6267b0d4e2be9fd4728c6a83b9c","tid":450574,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:03:13.000Z","msg":"其實多數派返同區考，住左十幾年應該都會知同區嘅學校點去掛"}]}